Use concise, imperative commit messages (e.g., fix: update login validation).

Write commit messages in Polish language.

Before commit message attach next version of application (ex. wersja 0.1.5.12).

All PRs must pass linter, formatter, and required checks.

Review according to above architecture and style guide.